De_Deposit-Army     (Bomb/Defuse Mission)

Hello guys! This is my first map. I hope you will enjoy. 

Description:
Story: The leader of a large terrorist group was arrested and convicted to jail. To take revenge, the terrorists planed to attack one of the state's main military assets.

Counter-terrorists: Careful! The weapons and ammunition depot is attacked by terrorists.

CT Notes: There was a big balloon with a trotyl in the room of the deposit. Careful! Do not press the red button in the control room!

Terrorists: Main Point A is in the secondary room of the weapons depot. Point B is in the control room.

Credits:
Bucsa Vlad – main level design
Dmitry Ghervas – mentor
